after its bottled.

15:24.205 --> 15:27.573
>> the councilman has
a fine palate.

15:27.641 --> 15:29.008
>> you know, we'd like to review
his purchases

15:29.076 --> 15:30.311
In the last six months.

15:30.379 --> 15:32.382
>> [laughing] we can't disclose
this information.

15:32.450 --> 15:36.391
>> unless we shut you down
for a forensic audit.

15:36.459 --> 15:41.831
>> [in bad french accent]
a print-out would do, huh?

15:41.899 --> 15:43.332
Coupla e-mails here

15:43.400 --> 15:45.334
Where the wine buddies
are talking

15:45.402 --> 15:48.104
About a '97 rioja.

15:48.172 --> 15:49.439
The councilman never ordered
any rioja.

15:49.507 --> 15:51.541
>> well, same thing
as the jeunesse cab.

15:51.608 --> 15:52.775
He never purchased it.

15:52.843 --> 15:54.776
>> it's a code.

15:56.578 --> 16:00.048
>> looks like
our vehicle canvass paid off.

16:00.115 --> 16:04.119
An '06 black van was ticketed
for blocking a driveway

16:04.186 --> 16:08.355
Ha a block from stacy's place
at 3:28 a.M.

16:10.256 --> 16:12.554
Security cameras picked up
an illegal port entry

16:12.621 --> 16:15.523
Eight blocks away
from stacy's place.

16:15.590 --> 16:19.826
Same late model black van
at 3:46 a.M.

16:19.894 --> 16:23.596
>> so the killer shoots siebert.

16:23.664 --> 16:25.731
15 minutes later,
he parks his van

16:25.799 --> 16:27.999
By the river
and dumps the weapon.

16:28.067 --> 16:30.068
>> yeah.
We'll get the divers on it.

16:30.135 --> 16:31.202
>> registration?

16:31.269 --> 16:32.369
>> the van is registered

16:32.437 --> 16:36.072
To a toscano trucking company
