42:02.161 --> 42:04.196
>> oh, that can't surprise you.

42:04.264 --> 42:06.965
I'm sure he's done it before.

42:07.033 --> 42:08.133
>> and denied it.

42:08.201 --> 42:10.636
Your life is blessed
because of me.

42:10.704 --> 42:16.074
